{"word":"Maaseiah","slug":"maaseiah","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Maaseiah</b> <a href=\"#/H4271\">H4271</a><br/><a href=\"#/H4641\">H4641</a> <br/> 1. A Levite musician<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=18'>1Ch 15:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=15&verse=20'>1Ch 15:20</a><br/> 2. A captain of hundreds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=23&verse=1'>2Ch 23:1</a><br/> 3. An officer of Uzziah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=11'>2Ch 26:11</a><br/> 4. Son of Ahaz, slain by Zichri<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=28&verse=7'>2Ch 28:7</a><br/> 5. Governor of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=34&verse=8'>2Ch 34:8</a><br/> 6. The name of a number of priests of the exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=18'>Ezr 10:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=22'>Ezr 10:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=4'>Neh 8:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=8&verse=7'>Neh 8:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=12&verse=42'>Neh 12:42</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=21&verse=1'>Jer 21:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=29&verse=25'>Jer 29:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=37&verse=3'>Jer 37:3</a><br/> 7. A returned exile<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=15&chapter=10&verse=30'>Ezr 10:30</a><br/> 8. Father of Azariah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=3&verse=23'>Neh 3:23</a><br/> 9. One who sealed the covenant<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=10&verse=25'>Neh 10:25</a><br/> 10. A descendant of Pharez<br/> <a href='https: